{"tid":2353610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六旬漢聲稱受武漢肺炎影響遭收屋單野係謊言","createTime":"2021-01-05T00:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T03:49:22.000Z","uid":26770,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"37286b14ae447f769710524f94a77a6118716871","tid":2353610,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T00:58:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2353602/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2353602/page/1</a><br />\n原文討論<br />\n<br />\n條撚樣聲稱2020年1月初往內地拜祭父母,<br />\n因唔想隔離所以2020年12月1日返港<br />\n<br />\n<strong>足足空左間屋十一個月,浪費左大量社會資源,大家查下同區單位幾錢租</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">咪就係支那畜牲根本係鬼國有大屋照呃香港公屋,諗住去香港玩都有大地方住</span><br />\n<br />\n租hotel 貴,無廚房唔方便"},{"pid":"5f616fb777b18358db1a18cce2de618bf90fa757","tid":2353610,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T01:07:07.000Z","msg":"棺材房都5k<br />\n同埋一年唔交租全世界都收得<br />\n<br />\n我老實講公屋大量呢種撚屌支那租霸<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">班仆街覺得好少收屋所以拉得一日就一日,因為做定期有額外錢<br />\n而通常香港本地人會去老房攪自動轉帳防止交漏左租奶野</span>"},{"pid":"0d7c05e906088bc480f5caacf613cb46469b6baf","tid":2353610,"uid":169048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T01:16:30.000Z","msg":"推撚爆條仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693b0e3d6a789cb9b93255fe5cb462acd800d326","tid":2353610,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T01:17:28.000Z","msg":"如果係住hotel 或租樓<br />\n佢一早寧願隔離14日返左黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff86323e58d67c6908bfdfe469566ed0d6fb0af3","tid":2353610,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T01:21:35.000Z","msg":"一定要炒大<br />\n呢條撚樣空置成年仲完全唔交租有咩可能唔收樓<br />\n<br />\n<strong>先前大把中港車司機交足租唔見人一排都比老房踢左</strong>"},{"pid":"3c9092cbf1861209ccdf5e50d79b1433d46fad61","tid":2353610,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T01:25:07.000Z","msg":"可能佢有好撚多個父母呢<br />\n拜足一年"},{"pid":"c6249857d52343d4d265a7d33baae9e0898a2a76","tid":2353610,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T01:25:43.000Z","msg":"就算係支那有親戚,住三幾日就得<br />\n邊有人接濟你一年<br />\n<br />\n條老不死擺明係支那有大屋"},{"pid":"00daaba21f5c5fd387ed6d63c8fd594c3aee6db9","tid":2353610,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T01:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb3aa200379ccbf3d2ec2f8b99033cbca58c06f","tid":2353610,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T01:32:51.000Z","msg":"幫佢嗰個區議員咩政黨㗎？"},{"pid":"0c03a291d2d554c91a5896a224d51b8a8543fa87","tid":2353610,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T01:39:27.000Z","msg":"<del>專誠寫信給房屋署說明難處，他以為房屋署收到了信件，所以就沒有繼續留意；同時他指他的手機已經沒有通話費，所以聯絡不上房屋署。</del><br />\n<br />\n有本事寄信去香港<strong>點解唔寄信比屋企人/朋友要求代增值電話費</strong><br />\n我已經唔講online都交到錢因為賤老一定賴唔識用<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">封求情信根本係不存在的,條友係9up講大話,<br />\n賤老有無寄件的收條,用三通一達寄一定有?</span>"},{"pid":"d5de1859e6bd7c1176c335acc01a7681e741eb7d","tid":2353610,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T01:47:02.000Z","msg":"同埋唔計老房撈的人<br />\n正常人根本唔會即答到老房full address <br />\n你寫信寫ssp附近 房屋署係寄唔到<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">曉掃mon查老房full address 但又唔曉用手機app增值?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24bdbd3f68d5cebd3c877e5a9b788822ef00fef8","tid":2353610,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"5f616fb777b18358db1a18cce2de618bf90fa757","tid":2353610,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T01:07:07.000Z","msg":"棺材房都5k<br />\n同埋一年唔交租全世界都收得<br />\n<br />\n我老實講公屋大量呢種撚屌支那租霸<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">班仆街覺得好少收屋所以拉得一日就一日,因為做定期有額外錢<br />\n而通常香港本地人會去老房攪自動轉帳防止交漏左租奶野</span>"}}